      "content": "For a high-end luxury watch brand, your ideal consumer is likely a successful, established individual, often from established, affluent backgrounds. They value timeless craftsmanship, heritage, and exclusivity over fleeting trends. While wealth is the primary driver, their cultural background often leans towards established global elites who appreciate traditional markers of success. Focus on individuals who embody quiet confidence and generational wealth rather than overt displays of new money.",
